ngthen their tassels."},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Other mss add on their robes"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 9:20","book":"Mat","chapter":9,"verse":20,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 14:36","book":"Mat","chapter":14,"verse":36,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 6:56","book":"Mrk","chapter":6,"verse":56,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 8:44","book":"Luk","chapter":8,"verse":44,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 13:9","book":"Exo","chapter":13,"verse":9},{"label":"Dt 6:8","book":"Deu","chapter":6,"verse":8},{"label":"Dt 11:18","book":"Deu","chapter":11,"verse":18},{"label":"Mt 6:1","book":"Mat","chapter":6,"verse":1},{"label":"Mt 6:5","book":"Mat","chapter":6,"verse":5},{"label":"Mt 6:16","book":"Mat","chapter":6,"verse":16},{"label":"Mt 9:20","book":"Mat","chapter":9,"verse":20},{"label":"Mt 14:36","book":"Mat","chapter":14,"verse":36},{"label":"Mk 6:56","book":"Mrk","chapter":6,"verse":56},{"label":"Lk 8:44","book":"Luk","chapter":8,"verse":44}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Lit do all their works"},{"marker":3,"text":"Other mss add on their robes"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They love the place of honor at banquets, the front seats in the synagogues,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 11:43","book":"Luk","chapter":11,"verse":43,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 14:7","book":"Luk","chapter":14,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 20:46","book":"Luk","chapter":20,"verse":46,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 11:43","book":"Luk","chapter":11,"verse":43},{"label":"Lk 14:7","book":"Luk","chapter":14,"verse":7},{"label":"Lk 20:46","book":"Luk","chapter":20,"verse":46}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"greetings in the marketplaces, and to be called ‘Rabbi’ by people."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“But you are not to be called ‘Rabbi,’ because you have one Teacher,"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss add the Christ"},{"kind":"text","text":" and you are all brothers and sisters."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 9:5","book":"Mrk","chapter":9,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 10:51","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":51,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 1:38","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":38,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 1:49","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":49,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 11:8","book":"Jhn","chapter":11,"verse":8,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 3:1","book":"Jas","chapter":3,"verse":1,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 9:5","book":"Mrk","chapter":9,"verse":5},{"label":"Mk 10:51","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":51},{"label":"Jn 1:38","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":38},{"label":"Jn 1:49","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":49},{"label":"Jn 11:8","book":"Jhn","chapter":11,"verse":8},{"label":"Jms 3:1","book":"Jas","chapter":3,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss add the Christ"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Do not call anyone on earth your father, because you have one Father, who is in heaven."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mal 1:6","book":"Mal","chapter":1,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 6:9","book":"Mat","chapter":6,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 7:11","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mal 1:6","book":"Mal","chapter":1,"verse":6},{"label":"Mt 6:9","book":"Mat","chapter":6,"verse":9},{"label":"Mt 7:11","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You are not to be called instructors either, because you have one Instructor, the Messiah. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The greatest among you will be your servant."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 20:26–27","book":"Mat","chapter":20,"verse":26,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 9:35","book":"Mrk","chapter":9,"verse":35,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"3Jn 9","book":"3Jn","chapter":1,"verse":9,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 20:26–27","book":"Mat","chapter":20,"verse":26},{"label":"Mk 9:35","book":"Mrk","chapter":9,"verse":35},{"label":"3Jn 9","book":"3Jn","chapter":1,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Whoever exalts himself will be humbled, and whoever humbles himself will be exalted."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 29:23","book":"Pro","chapter":29,"verse":23,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 21:26","book":"Ezk","chapter":21,"verse":26,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 14:11","book":"Luk","chapter":14,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 18:14","book":"Luk","chapter":18,"verse":14,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 4:6","book":"Jas","chapter":4,"verse":6,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 4:10","book":"Jas","chapter":4,"verse":10,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 5:5","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":5,"letter":"g"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Pr 29:23","book":"Pro","chapter":29,"verse":23},{"label":"Ezk 21:26","book":"Ezk","chapter":21,"verse":26},{"label":"Lk 14:11","book":"Luk","chapter":14,"verse":11},{"label":"Lk 18:14","book":"Luk","chapter":18,"verse":14},{"label":"Jms 4:6","book":"Jas","chapter":4,"verse":6},{"label":"Jms 4:10","book":"Jas","chapter":4,"verse":10},{"label":"1Pt 5:5","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Woe to you, scribes and Pharisees, hypocrites! You shut the door of the kingdom of heaven in people’s faces. For you don’t go in, and you don’t allow those entering to go in."},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Some mss include v. 14: “Woe to you, scribes and Pharisees, hypocrites! You devour widows’ houses and make long prayers just for show. This is why you will receive a harsher punishment."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 23:15","book":"Mat","chapter":23,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 23:23","book":"Mat","chapter":23,"verse":23,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 23:25","book":"Mat","chapter":23,"verse":25,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 11:52","book":"Luk","chapter":11,"verse":52,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 23:15","book":"Mat","chapter":23,"verse":15},{"label":"Mt 23:23","book":"Mat","chapter":23,"verse":23},{"label":"Mt 23:25","book":"Mat","chapter":23,"verse":25},{"label":"Lk 11:52","book":"Luk","chapter":11,"verse":52}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Some mss include v. 14: “Woe to you, scribes and Pharisees, hypocrites! You devour widows’ houses and make long prayers just for show. This is why you will receive a harsher punishment."}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Woe to you, scribes and Pharisees, hypocrites! You travel over land and sea to make one convert,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 2:11","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 6:5","book":"Act","chapter":6,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 13:43","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":43,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" and when he becomes one, you make him twice as much a child of hell as you are!"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 2:11","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":11},{"label":"Ac 6:5","book":"Act","chapter":6,"verse":5},{"label":"Ac 13:43","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":43}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Woe to you, blind guides,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 15:14","book":"Mat","chapter":15,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 23:24","book":"Mat","chapter":23,"verse":24,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 1:16","book":"Act","chapter":1,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 2:19","book":"Rom","chapter":2,"verse":19,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" who say, ‘Whoever takes an oath by the temple, it means nothing. But whoever takes an oath"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 19:12","book":"Lev","chapter":19,"verse":12,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 30:2","book":"Num","chapter":30,"verse":2,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 23:21","book":"Deu","chapter":23,"verse":21,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:33","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":33,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 14:7","book":"Mat","chapter":14,"verse":7,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 26:63","book":"Mat","chapter":26,"verse":63,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 26:72","book":"Mat","chapter":26,"verse":72,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"text","text":" by the gold of the temple is bound by his oath.’"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit is obligated, also in v. 18"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 15:14","book":"Mat","chapter":15,"verse":14},{"label":"Mt 23:24","book":"Mat","chapter":23,"verse":24},{"label":"Ac 1:16","book":"Act","chapter":1,"verse":16},{"label":"Rm 2:19","book":"Rom","chapter":2,"verse":19},{"label":"Lv 19:12","book":"Lev","chapter":19,"verse":12},{"label":"Nm 30:2","book":"Num","chapter":30,"verse":2},{"label":"Dt 23:21","book":"Deu","chapter":23,"verse":21},{"label":"Mt 5:33","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":33},{"label":"Mt 14:7","book":"Mat","chapter":14,"verse":7},{"label":"Mt 26:63","book":"Mat","chapter":26,"verse":63},{"label":"Mt 26:72","book":"Mat","chapter":26,"verse":72}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit is obligated, also in v. 18"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Blind fools! For which is greater, the gold or the temple that sanctified the gold? "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Also, ‘Whoever takes an oath by the altar, it means nothing; but whoever takes an oath by the gift that is on it is bound by his oath.’ "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Blind people!"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss read Fools and blind"},{"kind":"text","text":" For which is greater, the gift or the altar that sanctifies the gift?"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 29:37","book":"Exo","chapter":29,"verse":37,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 30:29","book":"Exo","chapter":30,"verse":29,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 29:37","book":"Exo","chapter":29,"verse":37},{"label":"Ex 30:29","book":"Exo","chapter":30,"verse":29}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Other mss read Fools and blind"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore, the one who takes an oath by the altar takes an oath by it and by everything on it. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The one who takes an oath by the temple takes an oath by it and by him who dwells"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Kg 8:13","book":"1Ki","chapter":8,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Ch 6:2","book":"2Ch","chapter":6,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 26:8","book":"Psa","chapter":26,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 132:14","book":"Psa","chapter":132,"verse":14,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" in it. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Kg 8:13","book":"1Ki","chapter":8,"verse":13},{"label":"2Ch 6:2","book":"2Ch","chapter":6,"verse":2},{"label":"Ps 26:8","book":"Psa","chapter":26,"verse":8},{"label":"Ps 132:14","book":"Psa","chapter":132,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And the one who takes an oath by heaven takes an oath by God’s throne"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 17:16","book":"Exo","chapter":17,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 11:4","book":"Psa","chapter":11,"verse":4,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:34","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":34,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 8:1","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":1,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" and by him who sits on it."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 47:8","book":"Psa","chapter":47,"verse":8,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 19:28","book":"Mat","chapter":19,"verse":28,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 4:2","book":"Rev","chapter":4,"verse":2,"letter":"g"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 17:16","book":"Exo","chapter":17,"verse":16},{"label":"Ps 11:4","book":"Psa","chapter":11,"verse":4},{"label":"Mt 5:34","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":34},{"label":"Heb 8:1","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":1},{"label":"Ps 47:8","book":"Psa","chapter":47,"verse":8},{"label":"Mt 19:28","book":"Mat","chapter":19,"verse":28},{"label":"Rv 4:2","book":"Rev","chapter":4,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Woe to you, scribes and Pharisees, hypocrites! You pay a tenth of"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or You tithe"},{"kind":"text","text":" mint, dill, and cumin, and yet you have neglected the more important matters of the law —justice,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 15:22","book":"1Sa","chapter":15,"verse":22,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 33:5","book":"Psa","chapter":33,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 5:1","book":"Jer","chapter":5,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mc 6:8","book":"Mic","chapter":6,"verse":8,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Zch 7:9","book":"Zec","chapter":7,"verse":9,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 11:42","book":"Luk","chapter":11,"verse":42,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" mercy, and faithfulness."},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or faith"},{"kind":"text","text":" These things should have been done without neglecting the others. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Sm 15:22","book":"1Sa","chapter":15,"verse":22},{"label":"Ps 33:5","book":"Psa","chapter":33,"verse":5},{"label":"Jr 5:1","book":"Jer","chapter":5,"verse":1},{"label":"Mc 6:8","book":"Mic","chapter":6,"verse":8},{"label":"Zch 7:9","book":"Zec","chapter":7,"verse":9},{"label":"Lk 11:42","book":"Luk","chapter":11,"verse":42}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or You tithe"},{"marker":2,"text":"Or faith"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Blind guides!"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 15:14","book":"Mat","chapter":15,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 23:16","book":"Mat","chapter":23,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" You strain out a gnat, but gulp down a camel!"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 15:14","book":"Mat","chapter":15,"verse":14},{"label":"Mt 23:16","book":"Mat","chapter":23,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Woe to you, scribes and Pharisees, hypocrites! You clean the outside of the cup and dish, but inside they are full of greed"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or full of violence"},{"kind":"text","text":" and self-indulgence."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 7:4","book":"Mrk","chapter":7,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 11:39","book":"Luk","chapter":11,"verse":39,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 7:4","book":"Mrk","chapter":7,"verse":4},{"label":"Lk 11:39","book":"Luk","chapter":11,"verse":39}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or full of violence"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Blind Pharisee! First clean the inside of the cup,"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss add and dish"},{"kind":"text","text":" so that the outside of it"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Other mss read of them"},{"kind":"text","text":" may also become clean."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Other mss add and dish"},{"marker":3,"text":"Other mss read of them"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Woe to you, scribes and Pharisees, hypocrites! You are like whitewashed tombs,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 11:44","book":"Luk","chapter":11,"verse":44,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 23:3","book":"Act","chapter":23,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" which appear beautiful on the outside, but inside are full of the bones of the dead and every kind of impurity. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 11:44","book":"Luk","chapter":11,"verse":44},{"label":"Ac 23:3","book":"Act","chapter":23,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"In the same way, on the outside you seem righteous to people, but inside you are full of hypocrisy and lawlessness."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Woe to you, scribes and Pharisees, hypocrites! You build the tombs of the prophets and decorate the graves of the righteous, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and you say, ‘If we had lived in the days of our ancestors, we wouldn’t have taken part with them in shedding the prophets’ blood.’ "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:31","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So you testify against yourselves that you are descendants of those who murdered the prophets. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:32","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Fill up, then, the measure of your ancestors’ sins!"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 15:16","book":"Gen","chapter":15,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 7:51","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":51,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 2:15–16","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":15,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 15:16","book":"Gen","chapter":15,"verse":16},{"label":"Ac 7:51","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":51},{"label":"1Th 2:15–16","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:33","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Snakes! Brood of vipers! How can you escape being condemned to hell?"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit escape from the judgment of gehenna"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 3:7","book":"Mat","chapter":3,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:22","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 12:34","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":34,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 3:7","book":"Mat","chapter":3,"verse":7},{"label":"Mt 5:22","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":22},{"label":"Mt 12:34","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":34}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit escape from the judgment of gehenna"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:34","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"This is why I am sending you prophets,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 13:1","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 12:28","book":"1Co","chapter":12,"verse":28,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" sages, and scribes. Some of them you will kill and crucify, and some of them you will flog in your synagogues"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Ch 36:15–16","book":"2Ch","chapter":36,"verse":15,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 10:17","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":17,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 22:19","book":"Act","chapter":22,"verse":19,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" and pursue from town to town. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 13:1","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":1},{"label":"1Co 12:28","book":"1Co","chapter":12,"verse":28},{"label":"2Ch 36:15–16","book":"2Ch","chapter":36,"verse":15},{"label":"Mt 10:17","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":17},{"label":"Ac 22:19","book":"Act","chapter":22,"verse":19}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:35","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So all the righteous blood shed on the earth will be charged to you,"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Lit will come on you"},{"kind":"text","text":" from the blood of righteous Abel to the blood of Zechariah,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Ch 24:21","book":"2Ch","chapter":24,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Zch 1:1","book":"Zec","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" son of Berechiah, whom you murdered between the sanctuary and the altar."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 4:8","book":"Gen","chapter":4,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 11:4","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":4,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 3:12","book":"1Jn","chapter":3,"verse":12,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 18:24","book":"Rev","chapter":18,"verse":24,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Ch 24:21","book":"2Ch","chapter":24,"verse":21},{"label":"Zch 1:1","book":"Zec","chapter":1,"verse":1},{"label":"Gn 4:8","book":"Gen","chapter":4,"verse":8},{"label":"Heb 11:4","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":4},{"label":"1Jn 3:12","book":"1Jn","chapter":3,"verse":12},{"label":"Rv 18:24","book":"Rev","chapter":18,"verse":24}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Lit will come on you"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:36","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Truly I tell you, all these things will come on this generation."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 10:23","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":23,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 16:28","book":"Mat","chapter":16,"verse":28,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 24:34","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":34,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 10:23","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":23},{"label":"Mt 16:28","book":"Mat","chapter":16,"verse":28},{"label":"Mt 24:34","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":34}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:37","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Jerusalem, Jerusalem,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 13:34–35","book":"Luk","chapter":13,"verse":34,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" who kills the prophets and stones those who are sent to her. How often I wanted to gather your children together, as a hen gathers her chicks"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or as a mother bird gathers her young"},{"kind":"text","text":" under her wings, but you were not willing!"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 32:11","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ru 2:12","book":"Rut","chapter":2,"verse":12,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:12","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":12,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 13:34–35","book":"Luk","chapter":13,"verse":34},{"label":"Dt 32:11","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":11},{"label":"Ru 2:12","book":"Rut","chapter":2,"verse":12},{"label":"Mt 5:12","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or as a mother bird gathers her young"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:38","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"See, your house is left to you desolate."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Kg 9:7","book":"1Ki","chapter":9,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 64:11","book":"Isa","chapter":64,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 12:7","book":"Jer","chapter":12,"verse":7,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 22:5","book":"Jer","chapter":22,"verse":5,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Kg 9:7","book":"1Ki","chapter":9,"verse":7},{"label":"Is 64:11","book":"Isa","chapter":64,"verse":11},{"label":"Jr 12:7","book":"Jer","chapter":12,"verse":7},{"label":"Jr 22:5","book":"Jer","chapter":22,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:23:39","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For I tell you, you will not see me again until you say, ‘Blessed is he who comes in the name of the Lord’!”"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 118:26","book":"Psa","chapter":118,"verse":26,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 21:9","book":"Mat","chapter":21,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 118:26","book":"Psa","chapter":118,"verse":26,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 118:26","book":"Psa","chapter":118,"verse":26},{"label":"Mt 21:9","book":"Mat","chapter":21,"verse":9},{"label":"Ps 118:26","book":"Psa","chapter":118,"verse":26}],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783279621457}